11
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:05,900
Here.

12
00:02:06,150 --> 00:02:08,110
I...I...

13
00:02:08,949 --> 00:02:09,970
I'm just lying down all day

14
00:02:09,990 --> 00:02:11,170
