24
00:02:22,770 --> 00:02:24,700
Life is in the stillness.

25
00:02:26,260 --> 00:02:27,110
Just imagine.

26
00:02:27,110 --> 00:02:28,240
If I live over 10,000 years,

27
00:02:28,270 --> 00:02:29,620
