95
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:01,950
Please, Dr. Lu.

96
00:06:02,710 --> 00:06:03,540
Auntie.

97
00:06:03,810 --> 00:06:05,010
Don't worry.

98
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,230
Before the surgery,

99
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:07,890
