120
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,590
Sure.

121
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:55,240
If you have any questions,

122
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,700
feel free to ask me.

123
00:06:57,270 --> 00:06:57,900
Okay.

124
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,530
[Lu Yan]

125
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:00,420
Thank you.

