293
00:13:27,570 --> 00:13:28,280
Over there.

294
00:13:28,430 --> 00:13:29,280
I'll take you there.

295
00:13:29,310 --> 00:13:29,590
Let's go.

296
00:13:29,590 --> 00:13:30,320
Okay.

